{"type":null,"faqId":33232,"title":"为什么插入联通卡后，在3G网络上会周期性的出现掉网现象？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.s1{color:black;}\n.p1{margin-left:0.39375in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{margin-left:0.39375in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p3{margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">出现此问题的原因通常是由于该联通卡未开通4G业务导致。当手机处于4G信号覆盖区域时，手机会自动尝试去注册联通4G网络，但是由于该卡未开通4G业务，因此注册4G时会被网络拒绝从而导致短暂掉网。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">解决此问题的方法是，建议用户手动将4G开关关闭。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">关闭4G开关方法如下：</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">1.选择状态栏下拉列表，关闭4G。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=104195\" style=\"width:2.557639in;height:4.548611in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  >\n<span>* 图示仅供参考，具体操作请以手机实际界面为准。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>2.进入 设置-无线和网络-更多-移动网络-首选网络模式，设置为非4G的模式。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=104196\" style=\"width:2.1708333in;height:3.8583333in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=104197\" style=\"width:2.1770833in;height:3.86875in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=104198\" style=\"width:2.1819444in;height:3.8819444in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=104199\" style=\"width:2.1291666in;height:3.7868056in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  >\n<span>* 图示仅供参考，具体操作请以手机实际界面为准。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":138,"faqType":"网络与数据共享","useful":0,"unUseful":3,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"7934","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Network-Data-sharing","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1436748538000,"seriesProductName":"PLK-AL10,PLK-CL00,PLK-TL00,PLK-TL01H,PLK-UL00","visitedTimes":29,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"4G卡,信号,掉网,联通","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}